#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.logical_xor.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.logical\\_xor"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:1 of
msgid "Compute the truth value of x1 XOR x2, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算 x1 和 x2 的逻辑异或值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:6 of
msgid ""
"Logical XOR is applied to the elements of `x1` and `x2`.  They must be "
"broadcastable to the same shape."
msgstr "逻辑异或运算应用于 `x1` 和 `x2` 的元素。它们的形状必须可以广播为相同形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:9 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播后的形状一致。如果未"
"提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:14 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的原始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:19 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- Boolean result of the logical XOR operation applied to the "
"elements of `x1` and `x2`; the shape is determined by whether or not "
"broadcasting of one or both arrays was required."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 应用于 `x1` 和 `x2` 元素的逻辑异或运算的布尔结果；形状由是否需要"
"对一个或两个数组进行广播决定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:24 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`logical_and`, :py:obj:`logical_or`, :py:obj:`logical_not`, "
":py:obj:`bitwise_xor`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:27 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_xor.logical_xor:39 of
msgid "Simple example showing support of broadcasting"
msgstr "展示支持广播的简单示例"

